d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac98aaf56acda9ba2688de55b354b01420fff1ed","tid":219400,"uid":23531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T16:49:55.000Z","msg":"靚聲幾好 不過懶音問題都幾嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36a81b1963d0747b1d7ecb5cf0548157b3781d15","tid":219400,"uid":88125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打聲底好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我建議你唱返冇咁高音嘅歌效果應該會仲好，假音位有時幾緊，但係中音位就好靚好温柔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你意思係我啲假音可以放輕少少唱，即係多啲氣聲<br />\n定係你話我上假音上得有啲勉強？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實聽得出假音位係有啲勉強，有少少flat<br />\n可以練多啲高音，試下拉闊個音域<br />\n我以前唱畫心，海豚音嗰part都練咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fe9611867e707539158a65ee6a2f17fc98c38d","tid":219400,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-02T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整體ok<br />\n但最尾好似懶有技巧咁轉音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我承認嗰part轉音真係好突兀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}